result.name: Sen-Ryo

reviews.text: Incredible little place tucked on the third floor next to Central exit D2. This place was sensational, every bite was beautiful. The perfect amount of rice  to flavour. We ordered quite a few different things, but definitely don't miss the flounder and steamed egg dish!

For sushi this place was good. It had London prices and more options on the belt. However, I opted for the lunch special set menu which makes the deal much more worth it. It tasted good and was satisfying and filling. It’s a decent stop for a spot of lunch.

If you are looking for value for money this is the place to go. Sushi in HK is extremely expensive. SenRyo is not cheap but still more affordable than high end places and its quality at least justifies the price.

Convenient spot for a quick sushi meal. The quality is decent and the decor is comfortable. The sushi platter is my usual go-to item. They also have a conveyor belt with different types of sushi or food items.

One of my favourite places for sushi which won't break the bank. Spicy salmon gunkan and soft shell crab handroll are a must! The quality is always good and if you fancy a sip of something other than tea, there's draft beer and a nice range of sake available. Queueing time is shorter here compared with the one in IFC.

result.name: Ippudo HK

reviews.text: Either people have really high standards or I'm an easy grader. This place is a 5. It's a bit of a dive, but it's very consistent. You can ask for customization if you wish. I usually order the special (best value). I haven't had a better ramen in HK. Go for the booth and chill. Unlimited, self pour cold tea is nice too!
The ramen is great, but I do miss the exclusive recipe when the ramen dish involves cooked and boiled pork
Decent quality but small portions

We tried another location a few days ago and this location is no different, courteous and efficient service, comfortable setting and excellent food. The lunch set menu is a pretty good value. This location didn’t seem to use the QR code system and instead took orders verbally.
Got seated quite fast, can order through QR code. Food arrived fast and hot. Have bibs to keep clean. Place is tidy and clean. Payment is fast as well.
